Welcome to Taniti Island

Activities

Experience snorkeling in coral reefs, jungle hiking, and immersive cultural tours led by local Taniti guides.

Dining

Savor island cuisine including fresh seafood, tropical fruits, and beachside fine dining with a view.

Lodging

Relax in ocean-view resorts, eco-lodges nestled in the jungle, or family-friendly hotels near the coast.
